{"tid":2307641,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★伊利沙伯醫院一名醫生初確診 同院另有一名醫生確診，兩人曾一同乘搭地鐵下班","createTime":"2020-12-01T09:49:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T13:46:09.000Z","uid":19454,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f0b5a22e75b869c0e44bd4e307a6baa6640adddf","tid":2307641,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T09:49:42.000Z","msg":"伊利沙伯醫院一名組織病理學醫生初確診。同院另有一名醫生確診，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>目前未找到病源，而兩人曾一同乘搭地鐵下班</strong></span>，其間有傾談。確診醫生在上周四、五感到不適，自上周四已無上班，今日初確診的醫生，於昨日開始不適，即日留深喉唾液樣本後已歸家。當局會調查是否工作上受感染，會做清潔消毒，相關同事全部77人需檢測，大部份樣本已完成，沒有發現陽性個案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/555753/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0-%E4%BB%8A%E5%A2%9E82%E5%AE%97%E7%84%A1%E6%BA%90%E9%A0%AD23%E5%AE%97-%E6%97%A5%E5%87%BA%E5%BA%B7%E5%9F%8E%E7%AC%AC9%E6%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E7%9B%A4%E7%88%86%E7%96%AB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F555753%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2596%25B0-%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25A2%259E82%25E5%25AE%2597%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%25BA%2590%25E9%25A0%25AD23%25E5%25AE%2597-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25BA%25B7%25E5%259F%258E%25E7%25AC%25AC9%25E6%259C%259F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%259B%25A4%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%2596%25AB&d=3wrM%2FJom4zLweqSprMIx0ma%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=85712190\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/555753/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0-%E4%BB%8A%E5%A2%9E82%E5%AE%97%E7%84%A1%E6%BA%90%E9%A0%AD23%E5%AE%97-%E6%97%A5%E5%87%BA%E5%BA%B7%E5%9F%8E%E7%AC%AC9%E6%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E7%9B%A4%E7%88%86%E7%96%AB</a>"},{"pid":"5e8f11c213dd28d70f19a82a6020c6108643a284","tid":2307641,"uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T09:50:19.000Z","msg":"地鐵群組<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.